## Additional Information

### Project Description

This software is a comprehensive Model Context Protocol (MCP) server designed
for collaborative intelligence with Claude AI. It provides advanced memory
systems, session management, project analysis, and development tools.

### Key Features

- 39+ specialized bb7_ tools across 7 modules
- Persistent memory system with SQLite storage
- Session management with decision tracking
- Project analysis and health monitoring
- Security auditing and code analysis
- Web integration and file operations
- Shell tools and environment management

### Attribution

Built using:

- FastMCP framework by @jlowin
- Model Context Protocol by Anthropic
- SQLite for persistent storage
- Python 3.11+ runtime environment

